titles.title: A joint resolution to designate the week of February 7 through February 13, 1993, as "Travel Agent Appreciation Week".

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S738)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Judiciary.

bill.summary: 1/26/1993--Introduced. Designates the week of February 7 through 13, 1994, as Travel Agent Appreciation Week.
